-- UBS Says Orcel to Join Investment Bank as Co-CEO Effective July
-- B y   F r a n k   C o n n e l l y
-- 2012-03-22T17:04:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-22/ubs-says-orcel-to-join-investment-bank-as-co-ceo-effective-july.html
UBS AG (UBSN)  said it hired Andrea Orcel
from  Bank of America Corp. (BAC)  as co-chief executive officer of its
investment bank.  Orcel will take the position effective July 1, UBS said in
a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at 
